articles.headline: No coin flip this time to decide South Carolina vs. Texas
articles.description: The SEC Now crew breaks down the 1-seed Gamecocks against the 2-seed (but top-ranked team in the nation) Longhorns in the SEC Women's Basketball Tournament Championship Game.

articles.headline: Women's Champ Week 2025: tournament brackets, auto bids, more
articles.description: We're tracking all 31 women's college basketball 2025 conference tournaments in the lead up to March Madness.

images.name: Notre Dame 2024 Champ Week final celebration [1296x729]
images.caption: Notre Dame booked the ACC's automatic bid to the 2024 women's NCAA tournament. Can the Fighting Irish do it again in 2025?

articles.headline: Schaefer on his Texas players: 'They are all of my world'
articles.description: After a hard-fought win against the 3-seed Tigers, an emotional Vic Schaefer joins SEC Now to further explain how he appreciates the Longhorns' toughness and shows his passion for their competitive spirit.

images.name: Schaefer on his Texas players: 'They are all of my world'
images.caption: After a hard-fought win against the 3-seed Tigers, an emotional Vic Schaefer joins SEC Now to further explain how he appreciates the Longhorns' toughness and shows his passion for their competitive spirit.

articles.headline: Highlight: Texas holds LSU to season-low score in hard-fought semifinal win
articles.description: Madison Booker scores 25 as the 2-seed Longhorns smother the 3-seed Tigers in the foul-ridden defensive battle, clinching their first SEC champ game berth with a 56-49 win.

images.name: Highlight: Texas holds LSU to season-low score in hard-fought semifinal win
images.caption: Madison Booker scores 25 as the 2-seed Longhorns smother the 3-seed Tigers in the foul-ridden defensive battle, clinching their first SEC champ game berth with a 56-49 win.

articles.headline: Iriafen's 25 points send No. 2 Southern Cal past Michigan 82-70, into Big Ten title game
articles.description: — Kiki Iriafen scored 17 of her 25 points in the second half Saturday, JuJu Watkins added 20 points and each pulled down 11 rebounds to send No. 2 Southern California past fifth-seeded Michigan 82-70 and into the Big Ten championship game.

images.name: Avery Howell knocks down a three to push USC ahead
images.caption: JuJu Watkins sets up Avery Howell to drain a crucial 3-pointer to boost USC.

articles.headline: Booker leads No. 1 Texas past No. 9 LSU 56-49, setting up rematch with South Carolina for SEC title
articles.description: — Madison Booker scored 25 points, and No. 1 Texas held on to beat ninth-ranked LSU 56-49 on Saturday night to advance to the Southeastern Conference Tournament championship game.

images.name: Highlight: Texas holds LSU to season-low score in hard-fought semifinal win
images.caption: Madison Booker scores 25 as the 2-seed Longhorns smother the 3-seed Tigers in the foul-ridden defensive battle, clinching their first SEC champ game berth with a 56-49 win.

articles.headline: Vonleh pours in 37 points, No. 17 Baylor women dominate OT in 84-74 win over No. 21 Oklahoma State
articles.description: — Aaronette Vonleh scored a career-high 37 points and No. 17 Baylor had three different players hit 3-pointers in overtime to lead the Bears into the Big 12 Conference Tournament...
